      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、こんばんは\nTRINITYAiLEの天動瑠依です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good evening‚ everyone.\nThis is Rui Tendo from TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5199.999999999999,
          "startTime": 8.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "私達のライブに来てくれてありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for coming to our live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8667800267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 5.8667800267
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（良かった。いつもの天動さんだ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Good‚ it's the usual Tendo-san…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6365759849,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 13.7752155144
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 13.7752155144
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "ミクと同じステージに立って\n疑問が浮かんだんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Standing on the same stage as Miku‚\nI had a question in my mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 19.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "私の歌は、もしかしたらミクの歌ほど\nファンの心に届いてないんじゃないかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe my songs don't reach the fans' hearts\nas much as Miku's songs do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 28.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 28.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（心配していたけど……悩みは吹っ切れたようだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I was worried‚ but it seems like she has resolved her worries.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5699.999999999999,
          "startTime": 35.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 33.8884225464
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 35.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（……え？　天動さん？　ど、どうして）\n（ステージの途中で歌を止めたんだ……！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…Eh? Tendo-san? W-Why?)\n(She stopped singing in the middle of the stage…!?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 41.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……っ、あ……あの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah… Umm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 44.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（歌詞を忘れたのか？　まさか、あの天動さんが！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Did she forget the lyrics? No way‚ Tendo-san of all people!?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません、今日は緊張し過ぎたみたいで……\n本当に……ごめんなさい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm sorry. I was too nervous today…\nReally… I'm sorry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "気を取り直して次の曲、いきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's regain our composure and continue to the next song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 61.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（どんなベテランだって、歌詞が飛ぶことはある）\n（でも天動さんにしてはめずらしい。いや、初めてか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Even seasoned professionals can forget lyrics sometimes.)\n(But it's unusual for Tendo-san. No‚ is it the first time?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 71.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 71.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、申し訳ありません……\n私、とんでもないミスを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ {user}-san…\nI made a terrible mistake…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、誰にでもあることだよ\n気持ちを切り替えて、次のステージで挽回しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay. It happens to everyone.\nLet's switch gears and make up for it in the next stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "そう、ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ you're right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 86.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（簡単には、切り替えられないようだな）\n（今の天動さんに必要なのは……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It's not easy for her to switch gears.)\n(What Tendo-san needs right now is…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 92.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……天動さん、良かったら明日\nちょっと付き合ってくれないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Tendo-san‚ if it's alright with you‚ could you accompany me tomorrow?\n…Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……え？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 101.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 101.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 101.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "あの……{user}さん\nここって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… {user}-san.\nThis place…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちがもやもやしている時はここに来るんだっけ\nいつかみたいに、大声で発散してみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you're feeling unsettled‚ you come here‚ right?\nHow about releasing it all with a loud voice‚ like someday?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 114.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "もう！　恥ずかしいです！\nそのことは忘れて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh gosh! That's embarrassing!\nPlease forget about that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 119.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "すまない、冗談だ\nでも今日は涼しいし、気分転換になると思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ it was just a joke.\nBut it's cool today‚ and I thought it would be a change of mood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "……気を遣わせてしまって、すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry for making you worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "飲み物も買って来たんだ。ゆっくり話をしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also bought some drinks. Let's talk at ease.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 134
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、ミクと自分を比べて悩んでいたのか\n鈴村さんや奥山さんはなんて言ってるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ were you comparing yourself to Miku and worrying?\nWhat does Suzumura-san and Okuyama-san say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "実は、まだ相談してないんです\nもちろん、二人にも相談しようと思ったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I haven't discussed it with them yet.\nOf course‚ I intended to talk with them too‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 149.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしたら、私達の今までを\n否定することになりそうで、怖くて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it feels like denying everything\nwe've done so far‚ and I'm scared…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 156.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルには本当に沢山のファンがいて\n心から応援してくれている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE has so many fans‚\nwho support us from the bottom of their hearts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "ステージからファンの顔を見て、分かるんじゃないか？\n天動さんの歌声は、みんなに届いてるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can't you see it by looking at the fans' faces from the stage?\nYour singing voice reaches everyone‚ Tendo-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 168.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "頭では分っているつもりです\n私達の歌だって、ファンのみんなに届いてるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that in my head.\nOur songs also reach all the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、聴き続けてくれているんだって\n私達を応援し続けてくれてるんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why they keep listening to us.\nThey keep supporting us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "だったらどうして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then why…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、理屈じゃないんだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's not about reasoning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 185.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 189.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "私にとって、ミクとのステージは……\nそれくらい大きな衝撃だったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For me‚ being on stage with Miku…\nIt was such a big impact.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 195.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui020.m4a",
      "text": "今まであった実感と自信が、遠のいて……\n気持ちがふわふわしてしまってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The sense of reality and confidence I had before… faded away.\nMy feelings are floating and fluffy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 203.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui021.m4a",
      "text": "こんな気持ちのまま、ステージに立ち続けたら\nそれこそ優やすみれ、ファンのみんなに失礼です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I keep standing on stage with these feelings‚\nit would be disrespectful to Yu‚ Sumire‚ and all the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 211.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。やっぱり、用意しておいて良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. It was good to prepare after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "用意って、何をです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Prepare? Prepare for what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_05_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "天動さん、事務所に行こう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendo-san‚ let's go to the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
